<div id="wrapper"><h2><a href="/output/Page2.asp"><img alt="" height="70" src="../files/images/XM_logo.gif" title="XM London Digital Communication" width="162" /></a></h2><h2><img width="253" alt="A 360 degree offer" height="80" border="0" src="/files/images/XM_L3_About_360_shdr.gif" /></h2><p>Unlike many digital media companies we work in interdisciplinary teams with each team taking ownership for specific clients work. This approach means that there is a strong sense of pride and integrity in taking a holistic view of the project and all members of staff's expertise is leveraged on your behalf. It also means that the creative solution is designed to work with the technology and that from day one there are no nasty surprises.</p><p>Our staff are multi-disciplined, expert in their own field, but also comfortable with associated digital disciplines. Our programmers understand the issues faced by our account managers, just as our strategists understand the technical and creative implications of their advice and recommendations. Our creative and designers understand the importance of usability and accessibility as well as brand issues.</p><img class="hide" src="/files/images/clear.gif" width="1" height="1" alt="" />
